OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784035119
OL,3,CSafer homes for four million tenants
OL,4,Cwith quicker action on dangerous houses
OL,6,FSocial housing tenants will get more
OL,7,Frights to have serious problems dealt
OL,8,Fwith faster under new laws - following
OL,9,Fthe death of a two-year-old boy.
OL,11,FAwaab's Law will force landlords to
OL,12,Ffix more dangers like electrical
OL,13,Ffaults, pest infestations, and unsafe
OL,14,Fstairs in quicker timeframes for the
OL,15,Ffour million tenants living in social
OL,16,Fhousing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
