FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784035119
OL,3,CSafer homes for four million tenants
OL,4,Cwith quicker action on dangerous houses
OL,6,FIt is named after Awaab Ishak, who
OL,7,Fdied in 2020 from a respiratory
OL,8,Fcondition caused by prolonged exposure
OL,9,Fto mould in the social home his family
OL,10,Frented in Rochdale, Greater Manchester.
OL,12,FSince 27 October 2025, Awaab's Law has
OL,13,Frequired social housing landlords to
OL,14,Ffix dangerous damp and mould in strict
OL,15,Ftimeframes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784035119
OL,3,CSafer homes for four million tenants
OL,4,Cwith quicker action on dangerous houses
OL,6,FThe second phase will extend the
OL,7,Fregulations to include hazards that
OL,8,Fpose an immediate danger to social
OL,9,Fhousing tenants, under new rules that
OL,10,Fwill come into force from 30 November
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FThis move will address seven more
OL,14,Fhazards such as electrical faults,
OL,15,Frisk of falling, structural defects,
OL,16,Fexcess cold and heat, fire risks, and
OL,17,Fhygiene issues such as pest
OL,18,Finfestations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784035119
OL,3,CSafer homes for four million tenants
OL,4,Cwith quicker action on dangerous houses
OL,6,FLandlords will have to investigate the
OL,7,Fproblem within 10 working days of
OL,8,Fbeing notified, and repair all
OL,9,Femergency hazards within 24 hours of
OL,10,Freporting.
OL,12,FIf homes cannot be made safe within
OL,13,Fthe timeframes, alternative
OL,14,Faccommodation must be offered to the
OL,15,Fresidents.
OL,17,FHousing Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,18,F"Awaab's Law sends a clear message
OL,19,Fthat tenants' health and safety can
OL,20,Fnever be compromised.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784035119
OL,3,CSafer homes for four million tenants
OL,4,Cwith quicker action on dangerous houses
OL,6,F"This action will mean dangers have to
OL,7,Fbe dealt with quickly by law,
OL,8,Fprotecting tenants' rights to a safe
OL,9,Fand decent home."
OL,11,FThe third and final phase of Awaab's
OL,12,FLaw will be introduced in 2027,
OL,13,Fextending the fast response to all
OL,14,Fremaining hazards except overcrowding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
