OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784035119
OL,3,CSafer homes for four million tenants
OL,4,Cwith quicker action on dangerous houses
OL,6,FGavin Smart, Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FChartered Institute of Housing (CIH)
OL,8,Fsaid: "Extending Awaab's Law to these
OL,9,Fhazards is an important step towards
OL,10,Fsafer, healthier homes, and we welcome
OL,11,Fthe collaborative approach the
OL,12,Fgovernment has taken.
OL,14,F"This is about more than compliance;
OL,15,Fit is a culture of listening to
OL,16,Fresidents and acting on their
OL,17,Fconcerns, and that is the change we
OL,18,Fwant to help the sector deliver."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
